cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper is about a challenge on video object segmentation, which is a task related to computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The challenge also involves the use of machine learning (ML) techniques, which suggests cs.MM and cs.LG as likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the development of state-of-the-art techniques, which could fall under cs.AI. Finally, the paper includes an analysis of the results of the participants, which could be related to graphics (cs.GR).
